e^x = 1 + 1/2!*x^2 + 1/3!*x^3 + 1/4!*x^4 + 1/5!*x^5 + 1/6!*x^6 ...
e^x = Σ[n_1, inf] 1/n!*x^n

x must be in radians. 
cos(x) = 1 - 1/2!*x^2 + 1/4!*x^4 - 1/6!*x^6 + 1/8!*x^8 ...
cos(x) = Σ[0,inf](-1)^n*x^2n/(2n)!

sin(x) = x - 1/3!*x^3 + 1/5!*x^5 - 1/7!*x^7 + 1/9!*x^9 ...
sin(x) = Σ[0,inf](-1)^n*x^2n*x/(2n+1)!
